column16: Evan Gattis flies out to center fielder Jake Marisnick.
Freddie Freeman walks.   Jason Heyward to 2nd.
B.  J.   Upton strikes out swinging.
Jason Heyward singles on a ground ball to center fielder Jake Marisnick.   Jordan Schafer scores.
Jordan Schafer singles on a line drive to left fielder Christian Yelich.
Russell Martin singles on a ground ball to left fielder Christian Yelich.   Josh Harrison scores.    Starling Marte to 2nd.
Steve Ames intentionally walks Starling Marte.
Jose Tabata grounds out, third baseman Placido Polanco to first baseman Logan Morrison.
Clint Barmes out on a sacrifice bunt, first baseman Logan Morrison to second baseman Ed Lucas.   Josh Harrison to 2nd.
Josh Harrison singles on a ground ball to center fielder Justin Ruggiano.
Tony Sanchez grounds out, third baseman Placido Polanco to first baseman Logan Morrison.
Gaby Sanchez doubles (14) on a line drive to right fielder Giancarlo Stanton.
Pedro Alvarez grounds into a double play, second baseman Ed Lucas to shortstop Adeiny Hechavarria to first baseman Logan Morrison.   Neil Walker out at 2nd.
Neil Walker singles on a line drive to left fielder Christian Yelich.
Jason Kipnis grounds out, first baseman Logan Morrison to pitcher Steve Ames.
Nick Swisher strikes out on a foul tip.
David Wright flies out to center fielder Jake Marisnick.
